            <title>[PIG-2012] Comments at the begining of the file throws off line numbers in errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2012</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The preprocessor does not appear to be handling leading comments properly when calculating line numbers for error messages.  In the attached script, the error is reported to be on line 7.  It is actually on line 10.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
